{
  "stem": "18186.4",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 12.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So my husband find some-- a woman, a girl, a young girl who know how to dance.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So he got involved with her, and we went home.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So-- Just let me ask you this.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "When you were there and you saw a list of names, did you ever make an attempt to find out about your own real family?",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Not then.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Not then.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I could not.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I saw my family in Stepan.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I know they went to the-- and Stepan was far away from Berlin, far away.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I really, the honest truth, we talked about the family.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But the question was--",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I didn't even try.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I don't think so.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because actually, maybe now of course, of course now-- if-- it wasn't really normal or anything.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You know, you were here today, tomorrow in another place.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And then all of a sudden, you stopped.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So what we-- when we went-- my husband was-- he was still-- left-- he was left behind.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But with the three men and I, we went on.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And we stopped.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We supposedly were-- I told him that we're planning to stop in Munich.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But meanwhile we stopped in the English zone in Hanover.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then we went also to the Jewish committee, to-- to sign in, and then they gave us-- they gave us stamps, sort of like to go and to eat, to get-- to eat, to get food.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they gave us--",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In a restaurant.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was everything-- Germany was already, you could go in and buy.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "There was restaurants.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was-- it was a little-- it was not so-- that was not really like after the war.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It took a few months after that when we got there.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
